### ============================================================
### VARIÁVEIS — preencha após o login
### ============================================================

@base_url = http://localhost:5000/api/v1
@tenant_demo = concurso-demo
@tenant_platform = platform

### ── Tokens (cole após fazer login) ────────────────────────
@token_admin =
@token_producer =
@token_student =


### ============================================================
### HEALTH
### ============================================================

### Health básico
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### Health com DB
GET http://localhost:5000/health/ready


### ============================================================
### AUTH — SUPER ADMIN
### ============================================================

### Login super_admin
# @name login_admin
POST {{base_url}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Slug: {{tenant_platform}}

{
  "email": "admin@platform.com",
  "password": "Admin@123456"
}


### ============================================================
### AUTH — PRODUTOR
### ============================================================

### Login produtor
# @name login_producer
POST {{base_url}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Slug: {{tenant_demo}}

{
  "email": "produtor@concursodemo.com",
  "password": "Produtor@123456"
}


### ============================================================
### AUTH — ALUNO
### ============================================================

### Login aluno
# @name login_student
POST {{base_url}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Slug: {{tenant_demo}}

{
  "email": "aluno@teste.com",
  "password": "Aluno@123456"
}

### Me — dados do usuário autenticado
GET {{base_url}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token_student}}
X-Tenant-Slug: {{tenant_demo}}


### ============================================================
### AUTH — SEGURANÇA
### ============================================================

### Senha errada — deve retornar 401
POST {{base_url}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Slug: {{tenant_demo}}

{
  "email": "aluno@teste.com",
  "password": "senhaerrada"
}

### Tenant errado — deve retornar 404
POST {{base_url}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Slug: tenant-que-nao-existe

{
  "email": "aluno@teste.com",
  "password": "Aluno@123456"
}

### Aluno tentando logar no tenant errado — deve retornar 401
POST {{base_url}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Slug: {{tenant_platform}}

{
  "email": "aluno@teste.com",
  "password": "Aluno@123456"
}

### Refresh token
POST {{base_url}}/auth/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{token_student}}

### Forgot password
POST {{base_url}}/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Slug: {{tenant_demo}}

{
  "email": "aluno@teste.com"
}

### Forgot password — e-mail inexistente (deve retornar 200 igual)
POST {{base_url}}/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Slug: {{tenant_demo}}

{
  "email": "naoexiste@teste.com"
}

### Registro de novo aluno
POST {{base_url}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Slug: {{tenant_demo}}

{
  "name": "Pedro Novo",
  "email": "pedro@teste.com",
  "password": "Pedro@123456"
}

### Registro com senha fraca — deve retornar 400
POST {{base_url}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Slug: {{tenant_demo}}

{
  "name": "Pedro Novo",
  "email": "pedro2@teste.com",
  "password": "123"
}


### ============================================================
### TENANTS — apenas super_admin
### ============================================================

### Listar tenants
GET {{base_url}}/tenants/
Authorization: Bearer {{token_admin}}
X-Tenant-Slug: {{tenant_platform}}

### Criar novo tenant
POST {{base_url}}/tenants/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token_admin}}
X-Tenant-Slug: {{tenant_platform}}

{
  "name": "Curso de TI",
  "slug": "curso-ti",
  "plan": "pro",
  "admin_name": "Carlos TI",
  "admin_email": "admin@cursoti.com",
  "admin_password": "Admin@123456"
}

### Tentar criar tenant como aluno — deve retornar 403
POST {{base_url}}/tenants/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token_student}}
X-Tenant-Slug: {{tenant_demo}}

{
  "name": "Tentativa Indevida",
  "slug": "tentativa",
  "plan": "basic",
  "admin_name": "Hacker",
  "admin_email": "hacker@teste.com",
  "admin_password": "Hacker@123456"
}